== Commerce ==
The Pacific is a hotbed of overseas [[Ship transport|shipping]]. The top 10 busiest container ports, with the exception of Dubai's [[Port of Jebel Ali]] (9th), are in the Rim nations. They are home to 29 of the [[List of world's busiest container ports|world's 50 busiest container shipping ports]]:

