== Organizations ==

Various [[Intergovernmental organizations|intergovernmental]] and [[non-governmental organization]]s focus on the Pacific Rim, including [[APEC]], the [[East-West Center]], [http://www.sustainablepacific.org Sustainable Pacific Rim Cities] and the [[Institute of Asian Research]]. In addition, the [[RIMPAC]] [[naval exercise]]s are coordinated by [[United States Pacific Command]].

